data.description: WOW! ***Seller is offering $2,500 towards buyer's closing costs*** This well-maintained 3 bedroom 2 bathroom corner lot home is GREAT! Conveniently located close to amenities, schools, parks & public transportation. This affordable home has charm & space to grow. As you enter the front door you will appreciate the bright living room leading to the dining room & kitchen. The beautiful arched doorways make this home even more appealing adding character! The master bedroom-suite is separate from the other 2 bedrooms and has its own mini-split level. The sunroom/bonus room could easily be used as an office, flex-room or breakfast nook. Nice size fenced back yard w/ storage shed. Need more space? The clean unfinished basement offers the potential for additional living space, storage or recreational area, it's just ready for your personal touches. Just minutes away from Main Highways, Hospitals, Restaurants, Shopping, Scott AFB & Downtown St Louis! Welcome Home!
